    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and will require significant mechanical and cosmetic attention to be roadworthy. The engine has a noticeable knock and the transmission slips significantly between gears, indicating the need for major repairs. The body shows visible rust and several dents, while the interior has heavy wear and some tears in the upholstery. It is being sold as-is for parts or as a major project for someone with mechanical expertise.",
