    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to hit the road in style with this fantastic find! This vehicle is in good, reliable condition and has been clearly well-maintained over the years. It drives smoothly, looks great, and is more than ready for its next adventure with a new owner who appreciates a solid, dependable ride. It's a clean, honest car that offers a great balance of performance and value!",
