    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and represents a solid choice for a buyer looking for a reliable daily driver without the premium price of a showroom-ready car. While the mechanical components, including the engine and transmission, have been maintained and function as expected, the exterior does show its age with some paint chips, minor scratches, and slight fading on the hood. The interior is clean but shows typical wear on the upholstery and some minor scuffs on the plastic trim. It is a dependable car that prioritizes utility and value over perfect aesthetics.",
