    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved, making it the perfect companion for your daily commutes or weekend getaways. It runs great and is totally ready for its next adventure with a new owner! Feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin\u2014I\u2019d love to see it go to a good home.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. This example delivers a linear power band up to its 8,000 RPM redline, paired with a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory-calibrated M-variable differential lock. The chassis maintains its composure through updated bushings and a reinforced rear subframe, ensuring the MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension geometry remains true under lateral load. While showing honest signs of use consistent with its mileage, the compression across all cylinders remains within factory spec, and the cooling system has been overhauled for thermal efficiency. A visceral, high-revving driver\u2019s tool ready for the canyon or the track.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car in good condition. Regularly maintained. Clean title. All systems functional. Reliable daily driver.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic balance of performance and reliability, having been cared for with a meticulous eye for detail. The exterior paint retains a brilliant luster, though a close inspection will reveal a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger wheel, consistent with careful daily use. Inside, the cabin remains a serene environment; the leather upholstery is soft and free of cracks or stains, and the dashboard remains pristine with no sun damage. Every feature, from the heated seats to the premium audio system, is in full working order. Mechanically, the car is in excellent shape, benefiting from a strict adherence to the manufacturer\u2019s service schedule. We have recently performed a comprehensive multi-point inspection, which included a fresh oil change and a coolant flush. The tires have approximately 70% tread remaining, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. It delivers a smooth, quiet ride with no unusual noises or vibrations. This is a solid, honest car that is ready for its next chapter without needing immediate investment.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
